# Rinkhals build environment configuration
#
# Copy this file to .env and adjust for your setup.
# The devcontainer works out of the box without a .env file.
#
# For non-devcontainer builds, you need at minimum BUILDROOT_DIR pointing
# to a Buildroot 2023.02.6 source tree with patches applied.

# Root directory for all intermediate build outputs (files, bundle, swu, etc.)
# RINKHALS_BUILD_DIR=/rinkhals-build

# Buildroot source tree location
# BUILDROOT_DIR=/buildroot

# Buildroot download cache (defaults to $RINKHALS_BUILD_DIR/buildroot-dl)
# Override to share downloads across projects or place on a larger disk.
# BR2_DL_DIR=/rinkhals-build/buildroot-dl
